                    Our company was founded in 1999 in Amsterdam by Bart Kuyper and Jeroen Rijnen.
                    Today Daxx operates offices in Kiev, Dnepropetrovsk, Kharkov, Ternopyl, St. Petersburg, Chisnau, New York, and London in addition to our headquarters in Amsterdam.
                    We have established dedicated client teams with over 220 developers for more than 100 clients.
                    Our mission is to connect businesses with great software developers, quality assurance testers, HTML coders, business analysts, and any other IT professional our clients need.
